    javax.servlet.Filter

    public class SelfConfiguredStormpathFilter
extends StormpathFilter
    A StormpathFilter that self-configures itself by looking up Client, Application, and Config instances from the ServletContext. Default implementation when Dependency Injection is not available.

    1.0.0
